###### 1. What is the difference between private limited and public limited company? State one example for each type.

A private limited company is a closely held one and requires at least two or more persons, for its formation. 
For example, Petronas Sdn. Bhd. 

A public limited company is owned and traded publicly. It requires seven persons for its setup.
For example, Maybank Bhd.

 `https://keydifferences.com/difference-between-public-company-and-private-company.html`

###### 2. Why is Berjaya Sports Toto Berhad registered under Non-Shariah Compliant?

I think Toto is one of the example of gambling/betting and this is against the teaching of muslim, hence it is registered under Non-Shariah Compliant.

