###### 7.What is the most important part of an annual report?

I think the most important part is the financial statement to allow current and future investors to determine how the company has performed in past.

###### 8.You have RM 10,000 savings and want to purchase shares as an investment for earning side income. You have listed two potential companies and need to select one company to invest. Comparing Pentamaster Corporation Bhd. and ViTrox Corporation Bhd. Justify your investment choice.

Pentamaster. According to the link below, Pentamaster is a better investment choice in terms of its liquidity, growth and valuation.

